query:
INSERT INTO users (
                    fingerprint,
                    pincode,
                    username,
                    deposit_addr,
                    withdrawal_addr,
                    balance,
                    created_at,
                    last_login
                ) VALUES (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3,
                    $4,
                    $5,
                    $6,
                    $7,
                    $8
                )
                ON CONFLICT (deposit_addr) DO UPDATE SET deposit_addr = $4
                RETURNING *
